    "description": "Use for inline status indicators with semantic color. Preset combinations: Success (bg=#D4EDDA, color=#2E844A), Warning (bg=#FEF3CD, color=#DD7A01), Error (bg=#FED7D7, color=#BA0517). Common labels: ACTIVE, AT RISK, CRITICAL, COMPLETED, PENDING."
